Limited Merch still available ‼️ LINK IN BIO

node.text: Crazy to think I been doing the car stuff on IG for 8 years now 🤯 I should of dropped merch along time ago but we here now! Y’all been killing the drops so we made few extra this time. All this stuff is limited and never dropping again‼️ This gonna be the OG limited stuff once the actual brand is here. We just getting started LINK IN BIO

node.text: Birthday wishes going crazy, Thank you guys 🙏🏽 merch available! Link in bio‼️

node.text:
Blessed to make it another year 🎉 Can’t believe I’m 30 🤯 Baby face gang so it’s coo 🤣
NEW LIMITED MERCH DROP IS LIVE‼️
New Hoodie design, Snapback hat & Plate frames! Once it’s gone it’s gone! If you cop a hoodie & hat you get a free jet tag 🤙🏽 
Worldwide shipping 🌍 LINK IN BIO ‼️

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by @freshhkiicks on August 04, 2021. May be an image of text that says 'FVLL BOLT TVNE LIMITED EDITION FULL BOLT ON TUNE COLLECTION'.

node.text:
Leggo 🔥 Limited merch dropping tomorrow 3pm PST Birthday drop 🎁
If you want to get me a gift tmw just buy some Merch 😂
I will be picking 3 people for $100 credit for the store‼️ All you have to do is make a post of your car with hashtag #fbotunebroo 
I will pick my top 3 favorite builds by 10pm pst tonight & repost on my story!  Excited for the drop let’s sell out a 3rd time 🔥

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by @freshhkiicks on August 02, 2021. May be an image of car and text that says 'FVLL BOL N VNE LIMITED EDITION FULL BOLT ON TUNE COLLECTION'.

node.text:
Let’s gooo 🔥 Another limited drop coming this Thursday on my birthday August 5th 🎁
It’s hot as hell & I don’t know why but y’all go crazy over the hoodies so we got a new design dropping along with snap back hats & new plate frames 🔥 FuLLbOlT On TUnE * accent 💀😂 iykyk 
Link In bio to subscribe for email notification when it drops Thursday!

node.text: Shout out to my boy @armentuned for the retune 🔥Was running a little rich on the other tune, cleaned up the AFR feels much better. Car is fbo cam E85 stock blower put down 717/772TQ while pulling timing due to it being 100 degrees outside. I’ll get it back on the dyno when it’s cooler to get a true number. Can’t ask for more for a fbo stick car 👌🏽
